        <p>Although the Site has security measures in place to protect against unauthorized access to and the loss, misuse and alteration of information under our control, we cannot guarantee that such security measures will be sufficient, will not be breached, and that your PI, private information, or any other information we maintain may not be disclosed or otherwise accessed in an unauthorized manner. Certain information, including PI and private information, may be transmitted by you and to you by unsecured electronic mail. Although it may be illegal to intercept or disclose these messages, these transmissions are not secured.</p>
